Posts.Content: Jun 3, 2009 06:25PM KDinDC wrote: I know more about endometriosis than I ever wanted to.  (Kind of like breast cancer!)  You MUST read Dr. David Redwine's website.  He is a surgeon in Bend, Oregon whose practice is entirely focused on endometriosis.  You will find that most gynecologists know very little about this disease.  http://www.endometriosissurgeon.com Good luck!
